{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-js","path":"/operators/continuous-deployment/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3ab88fcf-7fb3-5e54-b995-8c1aecc013e8","html":"<h1 id=\"continous-deployment\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#continous-deployment\" aria-label=\"continous deployment permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Continous Deployment</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first/continuous-deployment\">This repository</a> contains an opinionated reference architecture to setup, manage and operate a continous deployment pipeline.</p>\n<h3 id=\"prerequisites\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prerequisites\" aria-label=\"prerequisites permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prerequisites</h3>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Kustomize 3.8.1+</li>\n<li>SOPS 3.4.0+</li>\n<li>KSOPS 2.1.2+</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Find more information on how to install the pre-requisites <a href=\"docs/manage_your_app_secrets.md\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>Ensure you have the key to decrypt secrets. Open an issue in this <a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first/continuous-deployment/issues\">repository</a> requesting access.</p>\n<h3 id=\"gpg-key-access\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gpg-key-access\" aria-label=\"gpg key access permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>GPG Key access</h3>\n<p>This repo encrypts secrets using a dev test key, you can find the test key in <a href=\"https://github.com/oindrillac/continuous-deployment/blob/master/examples/key.asc\">examples/key.asc</a> folder.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ base64 -d &lt; examples/key.asc | gpg --import</code></pre></div>\n<p>You will need to import this key to be able to decrypt the contents of the secrets using sops.</p>\n<p>Do NOT use this gpg key for prod purposes.</p>\n<h3 id=\"howtos\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#howtos\" aria-label=\"howtos permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Howtos</h3>\n<p>See <a href=\"docs/\">how-to index</a> for various various procedures and how-tos when interacting with ArgoCD.</p>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/continuous-deployment/blob/master/README.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"3ab88fcf-7fb3-5e54-b995-8c1aecc013e8"}},"staticQueryHashes":["117426894","3000541721"]}